import React from 'react' export default() => { return(

Professional Experience

Web Developer Intern

Jan 2020 - July 2020

Oxfam America, Boston, MA

  • Integrated Oxfam’s database with Hubspot and leveraged Nodejs and Python for CURD to enhance the productivity of email marketing
  • Maximized the user experience and user interface by redesigning and creating new templates on the existing Oxfam website using HTML
  • Designed several templates via JavaScript, HTML CSS for email marketing targeting a vast range of audience
  • Built various forms for Oxfam’s social cause including a fundraiser for emergency
  • Resolved various issues for cross-functional teams
  • Scrutinized user research and created reports for better accessibility of Oxfam America website

IOT Intern

Jan 2018 – Apr 2018

University of Mumbai,India

  • Devised and implemented the project called Automatic Street Light
  • Arduino processor, light sensor and LED were used
  • Automation of the streetlights based on threshold levels of the project
  • Assembled the data on ThingSpeak using Wi-Fi module,which could be utilized for maintenance of street light

Research Intern

Dec 2017 – Jan 2018

University of Mumbai,India

  • Researched on ‘Evaluation of Information System’ using goal-based, goal- free and criteria- based evaluation techniques with focus on intangible and tangible benefits evaluation, and IS Risk Investment
  • Utilized the evaluation criteria to streamline the effectiveness of the education system

Research Intern

Dec 2017 – Jan 2018

University of Mumbai,India

  • Analyzed PayPal services, performed SWOT Analysis on Payment Gateway and Electronic Data Interchange
  • Explored Customer Relationship Management, Enterprise Resource Planning, and Supply Chain Management Systems
  • Utilized the customer relationship management research to increase the profit
) }
